edu.buffalo.cse562.checkpoint1.eval

Interface AggregateImpl

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AggregateImpl.ArithmeticAggregate, AggregateImpl.Avg, AggregateImpl.Count, AggregateImpl.CountDistinct, AggregateImpl.Max, AggregateImpl.Min, AggregateImpl.Sum

    public interface AggregateImpl
    Implementations of most of the core aggregate methods. AggregateImpl.ArithmeticAggregate is an abstract superclass for distributive aggregates. AggregateImpl.Factory is a factory superclass.
